    {
      "id": "line-000",
      "start": 0.88,
      "end": 6.18,
      "text": "This is a Libervox recording. All Libervox recordings are in the public domain. For more",
      "note": ""
    },
    {
      "id": "line-001",
      "start": 6.18,
      "end": 12.66,
      "text": "information or to volunteer, please visit Libervox.org. This reading by Basil Munro Gadevanos.",
      "note": ""
    },
    {
      "id": "line-002",
      "start": 13.28,
      "end": 17.42,
      "text": "Be Munro.roestudios.com.",
      "note": ""
    },
    {
      "id": "line-003",
      "start": 19.72,
      "end": 23.24,
      "text": "The Flea and the Man. A fable of Asap.",
      "note": ""
    },
    {
      "id": "line-004",
      "start": 24.72,
      "end": 40.46,
      "text": "A flea bit a man and bit him again and again, till he could stand it no longer, but made a thorough search for it, and at last succeeded in catching it. Holding it between his finger and thumb, he said, or rather shouted so angry was he.",
      "note": ""
    },
    {
      "id": "line-005",
      "start": 41.0,
      "end": 45.52,
      "text": "Who are you, Prey, you wretched little creature, that you make so free with my person?",
      "note": ""
    },
    {
      "id": "line-006",
      "start": 46.94,
      "end": 50.76,
      "text": "The Flea terrified. Wimpered in a weak little voice.",
      "note": ""
    },
    {
      "id": "line-007",
      "start": 51.46,
      "end": 57.5,
      "text": "Oh sir, pray let me go, don't kill me, I am such a little thing that I can't do you much harm.",
      "note": ""
    },
    {
      "id": "line-008",
      "start": 58.26,
      "end": 66.52,
      "text": "But the man laughed and said, I am going to kill you now, at once. Whatever is bad has got to be destroyed no matter how slight the harm it does.",
      "note": ""
    },
    {
      "id": "line-009",
      "start": 68.36,
      "end": 75.48,
      "text": "Do not waste your pity on a scam. End of the Flea and the Man.",
      "note": ""
    },
    {
      "id": "line-010",
      "start": 76.62,
      "end": 82.34,
      "text": "Recorded on January 24th, 2006, in Newmarket, Ontario, Canada.",
      "note": ""
    }
  ],
